# Trivy False Positives — documented and verified

#

# Helm trusted registry validation is enforced at template render time via

# the `nexus-hems.assertTrustedImageRepository` helper in \_helpers.tpl.

# Trivy cannot evaluate Helm templates and reports these as misconfigurations.

# See: helm/nexus-hems/templates/\_helpers.tpl (assertTrustedImageRepository)

# #174 — deployment-frontend.yaml: image validated by nexus-hems.imageRef helper

# #175 — deployment-server.yaml: image validated by nexus-hems.imageRef helper

